column1: #Text=Responsibilities: Interact with our Databricks datalake to develop meaningful recommendation APIs for our customers.

#Text=Develop end-to-end solutions that leverage our message based architecture and deep integration with key AWS services to automate using tools like Lambda, Eventbridge, Systems Manager, terraform, and Helm.
